                        <provenance type="observed" when="2014">The stone is now lying on the ground outside the rath at the SW. Accoding to the landowner, it had fallen from the bank some time ago. When visiting the site to scan the ogham stones in July 2014 this ogham stone was found lying on the ground outside the bank of the ringfort. The local OPW rolled the stone over at this time so that the inscription on the second angle could be recorded.
